<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p><big>It’s a wrap!</big> We were giddy with excitement for this year’s JCK. As a fine jewellery manufacturer from Hong Kong, this show was a perfect platform to showcase our new creative jewellery pieces, as well as to gain insight from global industry experts on emerging latest jewellery trends and technology innovations. Again, 4 dazzling days at JCK were a vibrant and memorable experience. Fabulous times, indeed!</p><p>With a dynamic range of exhibitors from around the globe gathering at JCK, the show provided an unparalleled window into the world of modern jewellery. To stay ahead of the jewellery trends and maintain our momentum as a creative jeweller, JCK offered us to see what’s set to be trending in the market. We are back with more of everything. Here, we offer our insights into what we discovered – at JCK – not to be missed.</p>'=>'<p><big>就这么定了！</big> 我们对今年的 JCK 感到非常兴奋。作为一家来自香港的高级珠宝制造商，这次展会为我们提供了一个绝佳的平台，让我们展示最新的创意珠宝作品，并从全球行业专家那里了解最新的珠宝趋势和技术创新。同样，在 JCK 的 4 天令人眼花缭乱，充满活力，令人难忘。这的确是一段美妙的时光！   </p><p>来自全球各地的参展商齐聚 JCK，为我们提供了一个了解现代珠宝世界的无与伦比的窗口。为了走在珠宝潮流的前端，保持我们作为创意珠宝商的势头，JCK 为我们提供了了解市场流行趋势的机会。我们带着更多的东西回来了。在此，我们将为您介绍我们在 JCK 上发现的不容错过的真知灼见。   </p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_dark" style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: normal;">22-24 Jun (Thu-Sat) 1000-1800</span><br><span class="trx_addons_dark" style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: normal;">25 Jun (Sun) 1000-1700</span><br></p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_dark" style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: normal;">6 月 22-24 日（周四至周六） 1000-1800</span><br><span class="trx_addons_dark" style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: normal;">6 月 25 日（周日） 1000-1700</span><br></p>','<p><strong><big>Follow us</big></strong></p>'=>'<p><strong><big>关注我们</big></strong></p>','<p>Another trend is the use of bold, vibrant colours, featuring fun and playful designs. We recognized a rise in coloured stone jewellery, and there is no doubt that coloured gemstones are here to stay. Bright and optimistic colours from coloured gemstones add a touch of personality to everyone and bring glamour and an uplifting spirit to the style.</p>'=>'<p>另一个趋势是使用大胆、鲜艳的色彩，以有趣、好玩的设计为特色。我们认识到彩色宝石珠宝的兴起，毫无疑问，彩色宝石将继续流行。彩色宝石明亮而乐观的色彩为每个人增添了一抹个性，为风格带来了魅力和振奋人心的精神。  </p>','<p>Booth 1C-302, Hong Kong Convention &amp; Exhibition Centre (HKCEC)<br />1 Expo Drive, Wanchai, Hong Kong</p>'=>'<p>香港湾仔博览道 1 号香港会议展览中心（HKCEC）1C-302 展位<br></p>','<p>Diamond fashion jewellery is always a modern classic. Fashion jewellery is more than just an accessory; the timeless beauty of diamonds will always be style and add sparkle to the modern jewellery designs. We spotted some exciting new trends at JCK – a modern twist from classic design styles. The return of stacking and layering is a great way to embrace the timeless elegance and style.</p>'=>'<p>钻石时尚珠宝永远是现代经典。时尚珠宝不仅仅是一种配饰；钻石的永恒之美永远是时尚的风格，并为现代珠宝设计增添光彩。我们在 JCK 上发现了一些令人兴奋的新趋势--经典设计风格的现代转折。堆叠和层叠的回归是体现永恒优雅和风格的绝佳方式。   </p>','<p>Discover our range of<a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/ejimain/"> textured jewellery</a> creations that celebrate the richness and versatility of our craftmanship and creativity.</p>'=>'<p>探索我们的<a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/ejimain/"> 纹理珠宝</a>系列，欣赏我们丰富多变的工艺和创意。</p>','<p>Please register at the <a href="https://onlinereg.informamarkets-info.com/Login.aspx?Lang=en&amp;EventID=20236JG&amp;utm_medium=Website&amp;utm_source=JGA23_website_header_EN&amp;utm_campaign=202306JGA_VP_JGA23_vis_reg_JGA_web_header_EN&amp;utm_content=JGA23_website_header_vis_reg_EN&amp;sor=JGA23_website_header_EN">JGA official site</a>!</p>'=>'<p>请在<a href="https://onlinereg.informamarkets-info.com/Login.aspx?Lang=en&amp;EventID=20236JG&amp;utm_medium=Website&amp;utm_source=JGA23_website_header_EN&amp;utm_campaign=202306JGA_VP_JGA23_vis_reg_JGA_web_header_EN&amp;utm_content=JGA23_website_header_vis_reg_EN&amp;sor=JGA23_website_header_EN">JGA 官方网站</a>注册！</p>','<p>The charm of coloured stone jewellery is hard to resist. We are also here to celebrate this cheerful and colorful vibe with a range of creative jewellery collections.</p>'=>'<p>彩石珠宝的魅力难以抗拒。我们也在此推出一系列创意珠宝系列，为这一欢快多彩的氛围喝彩。 </p>','<p>This year’s fair highlighted a clear focus on minimalist yet distinctive designs that celebrate craftsmanship through metal finishing techniques. Gold jewellery never goes out of style. It will continue and add exquisite craftsmanship to give it a modern edge through textured metal finishing like brushing, hammering or microblasting. Metal finishing adds style and a bold statement of contrasts to every piece of jewellery creation, and gains popularity for a more understated yet elegant and aesthetic.</p>'=>'<p>今年的珠宝展重点突出简约而独特的设计，通过金属表面处理技术来弘扬手工艺。金饰永不过时。它将继续延续并加入精湛的工艺，通过拉丝、锤击或微喷等纹理金属表面处理，赋予其现代优势。金属表面处理为每一件珠宝作品都增添了风格和大胆的对比，并因其低调而优雅的美感而广受欢迎。   </p>','<p>Visit <a href="http://www.jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com"><strong><em>jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com</em></strong></a> to learn more about the show’s events.</p>'=>'<p>访问 <a href="http://www.jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com"><strong><em>jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com</em></strong></a>了解更多展会活动信息。</p>','<p>We come in a wide range of stunning diamond fashion jewellery pieces, from understated and simple to eye-catching and bold. Let’s check out our <a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/ejimain/">newest collection</a> that brings effortless chic styles.</p>'=>'<p>我们有各种令人惊叹的时尚钻石首饰，从低调简约到醒目大胆，应有尽有。让我们一起来看看我们的<a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/ejimain/">最新系列</a>，轻松打造别致风格。 </p>','<p>When you’re plotting your show agenda for upcoming <strong>Hong Kong Jewellery &amp; Gem Asia Fair</strong>, keep all these keynotes in mind. As a local-based B2B jewellery company in Hong Kong, we couldn’t be more excited to be exhibiting at this Asia’s biggest mid-year B2B fine jewellery trade fair.</p><p>This mid-year JGA 2023 marks the first comeback after the three-year pandemic, and we are ready to welcome all of you. From classic diamonds to bold and creative jewellery, we have got everything that keeps up to date with the expected jewellery trends. With us, you can always share your own ideas and enjoy our unique bespoke jewellery services.</p>'=>'<p>当您为即将到来的<strong>香港亚洲珠宝首饰展览会</strong>制定展会日程时，请牢记这些主题演讲。作为香港本地的 B2B 珠宝公司，我们非常高兴能参加这个亚洲最大的年中 B2B 高级珠宝贸易展览会。 </p><p>今年年中的 JGA 2023 标志着三年大流行后的首次回归，我们已准备好迎接大家的到来。从经典的钻石到大胆创新的珠宝，我们拥有一切与时俱进的珠宝潮流。在我们这里，您可以随时分享自己的创意，享受我们独一无二的定制珠宝服务。  </p>','<span style="color: var(--theme-color-text_dark); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.15em; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color);">INSIGHT 2:</span> Diamond Forever'=>'<span style="color: var(--theme-color-text_dark); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.15em; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color);">洞察 2：</span>钻石恒久远','Book Your Appointment'=>'预约','INSIGHT 3: Colour Flash'=>'INSIGHT 3：彩色闪光','Insight 1: Texture fever'=>'启示 1：纹理热','Location'=>'地点','Registration'=>'注册','Show Hours'=>'演出时间','dailymotion_url-video-67ce21f'=>'https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6tqhqb','editor-text-editor-139bc42'=>'<p>今年的珠宝展重点突出简约而独特的设计，通过金属表面处理技术来弘扬手工艺。金饰永不过时。它将继续延续并加入精湛的工艺，通过拉丝、锤击或微喷等纹理金属表面处理，赋予其现代优势。金属表面处理为每一件珠宝作品都增添了风格和大胆的对比，并因其低调而优雅的美感而广受欢迎。   </p>','editor-text-editor-199946b'=>'<p><strong><big>关注我们</big></strong></p>','editor-text-editor-2d7aab1'=>'<p>彩石珠宝的魅力难以抗拒。我们也在此推出一系列创意珠宝系列，为这一欢快多彩的氛围喝彩。 </p>','editor-text-editor-668be6f'=>'<p>钻石时尚珠宝永远是现代经典。时尚珠宝不仅仅是一种配饰；钻石的永恒之美永远是时尚的风格，并为现代珠宝设计增添光彩。我们在 JCK 上发现了一些令人兴奋的新趋势--经典设计风格的现代转折。堆叠和层叠的回归是体现永恒优雅和风格的绝佳方式。   </p>','editor-text-editor-6a77b51'=>'<p>另一个趋势是使用大胆、鲜艳的色彩，以有趣、好玩的设计为特色。我们认识到彩色宝石珠宝的兴起，毫无疑问，彩色宝石将继续流行。彩色宝石明亮而乐观的色彩为每个人增添了一抹个性，为风格带来了魅力和振奋人心的精神。  </p>','editor-text-editor-7bd2f7f'=>'<p>访问 <a href="http://www.jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com"><strong><em>jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com</em></strong></a>了解更多展会活动信息。</p>','editor-text-editor-a8652b7'=>'<p>当您为即将到来的<strong>香港亚洲珠宝首饰展览会</strong>制定展会日程时，请牢记这些主题演讲。作为香港本地的 B2B 珠宝公司，我们非常高兴能参加这个亚洲最大的年中 B2B 高级珠宝贸易展览会。 </p><p>今年年中的 JGA 2023 标志着三年大流行后的首次回归，我们已准备好迎接大家的到来。从经典的钻石到大胆创新的珠宝，我们拥有一切与时俱进的珠宝潮流。在我们这里，您可以随时分享自己的创意，享受我们独一无二的定制珠宝服务。  </p>','editor-text-editor-b81cfc8'=>'<p><big>就这么定了！</big> 我们对今年的 JCK 感到非常兴奋。作为一家来自香港的高级珠宝制造商，这次展会为我们提供了一个绝佳的平台，让我们展示最新的创意珠宝作品，并从全球行业专家那里了解最新的珠宝趋势和技术创新。同样，在 JCK 的 4 天令人眼花缭乱，充满活力，令人难忘。这的确是一段美妙的时光！   </p><p>来自全球各地的参展商齐聚 JCK，为我们提供了一个了解现代珠宝世界的无与伦比的窗口。为了走在珠宝潮流的前端，保持我们作为创意珠宝商的势头，JCK 为我们提供了了解市场流行趋势的机会。我们带着更多的东西回来了。在此，我们将为您介绍我们在 JCK 上发现的不容错过的真知灼见。   </p>','editor-text-editor-c7221f2'=>'<p>我们有各种令人惊叹的时尚钻石首饰，从低调简约到醒目大胆，应有尽有。让我们一起来看看我们的<a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/ejimain/">最新系列</a>，轻松打造别致风格。 </p>','editor-text-editor-d6e80e0'=>'<p>探索我们的<a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/ejimain/"> 纹理珠宝</a>系列，欣赏我们丰富多变的工艺和创意。</p>','https://vimeo.com/235215203'=>'https://vimeo.com/235215203','https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6tqhqb'=>'https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6tqhqb','https://youtu.be/8iSRo8Z1l78'=>'https://youtu.be/8iSRo8Z1l78','mailto:sales@x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site'=>'mailto:sales@x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site','text-button-d03948d'=>'预约','title-heading-1f0dea1'=>'启示 1：纹理热','title-heading-879c942'=>'<span style="color: var(--theme-color-text_dark); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.15em; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color);">洞察 2：</span>钻石恒久远','title-heading-b1db7fc'=>'INSIGHT 3：彩色闪光','toggle-tab_content-5884f4d-1424e35'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_dark" style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: normal;">6 月 22-24 日（周四至周六） 1000-1800</span><br><span class="trx_addons_dark" style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: normal;">6 月 25 日（周日） 1000-1700</span><br></p>','toggle-tab_content-5884f4d-44eb715'=>'<p>请在<a href="https://onlinereg.informamarkets-info.com/Login.aspx?Lang=en&amp;EventID=20236JG&amp;utm_medium=Website&amp;utm_source=JGA23_website_header_EN&amp;utm_campaign=202306JGA_VP_JGA23_vis_reg_JGA_web_header_EN&amp;utm_content=JGA23_website_header_vis_reg_EN&amp;sor=JGA23_website_header_EN">JGA 官方网站</a>注册！</p>','toggle-tab_content-5884f4d-a702809'=>'<p>香港湾仔博览道 1 号香港会议展览中心（HKCEC）1C-302 展位<br></p>','toggle-tab_title-5884f4d-1424e35'=>'演出时间','toggle-tab_title-5884f4d-44eb715'=>'注册','toggle-tab_title-5884f4d-a702809'=>'地点','url-button-d03948d'=>'mailto:sales@x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site','vimeo_url-video-67ce21f'=>'https://vimeo.com/235215203','youtube_url-video-67ce21f'=>'https://youtu.be/8iSRo8Z1l78']];
